    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-band">
    <h2>What belongs here</h2>
    <p>
      The blog is for thoughts, technical notes, learning reflections, and small
      essays. The site can grow over time with project pages, reading notes, and a
      clearer archive as the writing accumulates.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
